1. *Guraj* kofere u automobil. (Push the suitcases into the car.)
2. Ne mogu sama, *gurni* me malo. (I can't do it alone, give me a little push.)
3. Ako *gurnemo* malo ovaj sto, mogli bismo staviti jos jednu stolicu. (If we move this table a bit, we could put another chair.)
4. On je bio taj koji je *gurao* tim tokom citave utakmice. (He was the one who pushed the team throughout the whole game.)
5. Nemoj *gurati* decu u blatu, zabrljace se. (Don't push the kids into the mud, they will get dirty.)
6. *Gurajuci* bicikl, osetio je da mu guma puca. (While pushing the bike, he felt the tire pop.)
7. *Gurajte* jos malo, pa cemo biti tamo. (Push a little more, and we will be there.)
8. Oni su *gurali* kola po snegu dok ih nisu izvukli iz jarka. (They pushed the car through the snow until they got it out of the ditch.)
9. Molim te, *gurni* ovu knjigu ka meni. (Please, push this book towards me.)
10. Ljudi su *gurali* jedni druge kako bi se dokopali poslednjeg vagona. (People were pushing each other to get to the last carriage.)

(Note: The word "guraj" in Serbian can be translated to "push" in English.)